One night, Oscar invites Linda to a club and&nbsp;
asks her to try a drug. After taking the pill,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:04.560 --> 00:07:09.360
Linda starts dancing sensually and invites Alex&nbsp;
to join her. When Alex refuses, Mario approaches&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:13.840
Linda and gives her a card. Linda and Mario spend&nbsp;
some time together drinking as Oscar talks with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:13.840 --> 00:07:18.160
Victor about scoring some drugs. When he takes&nbsp;
Linda home, he notices that she got very drunk.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:22.720
