Oscar feels very protective of her,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:43.200
so he visits her at work and tells&nbsp;
Mario not to touch her. Mario, however,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:45.440
brushes him off and tells him&nbsp;
not to act like a bad brother.

