While scoring some pills from Bruno, Oscar&nbsp;
suddenly mentions that he's sharing them&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:53.440
with Victor. Bruno, who’s very paranoid about&nbsp;
getting caught, dissuades Oscar from mentioning&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:57.280
his friend to him or telling his friend about&nbsp;
him. In the strip club, Oscar offers some drugs&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:57.280 --> 00:08:01.760
to the girls inside the dressing room. Not long,&nbsp;
Mario arrives and castigates Oscar for selling&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:01.760 --> 00:08:05.920
pills to the dancers. Mario threatens to kill&nbsp;
Oscar if he ever sees him inside the club again.

00:08:06.640 --> 00:08:09.680
Oscar gets furious with Linda when&nbsp;
she fails to come home one night.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:13.920
He asks Linda to inform him whenever she&nbsp;
spends time with Mario. Linda, however,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:17.680
