asks Oscar if he’s jealous of her boss.

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:22.160
Bruno meets with Oscar outside to give him some&nbsp;
ecstasy and tell him that he has some D.M.T. After&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:26.480
getting the pills, Oscar stops by Victor's house&nbsp;
