on the phone, Oscar flies to Alex's apartment&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:22.720
while the police search for clues about his&nbsp;
location. After the search, the cops interrogate&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:22.720 --> 00:09:25.840
Victor and threaten him with jail time if he&nbsp;
doesn't tell them what he knows about Alex.

00:09:26.560 --> 00:09:30.240
A few days later, Linda takes a&nbsp;
pregnancy test and asks Alex's friend,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:35.040
Saki, to read the result because it's in Japanese.&nbsp;
After taking a look, Saki reluctantly tells her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:35.040 --> 00:09:40.160
that it's positive. At the strip club, Mario meets&nbsp;
with Bruno and asks for some coke. Bruno tells him&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:40.160 --> 00:09:43.680
that he got rid of all his drugs because he fears&nbsp;
Victor might have mentioned him to the police.

