Oscar floats to Victor's home and finds&nbsp;
Suzy berating Victor for calling the cops.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:48.160 --> 00:09:51.920
As the argument escalates, Victor tells his&nbsp;
father that Suzy slept with his best friend.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:54.560
Victor's dad hits him and tells&nbsp;
him to get out of the house.

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:59.840
When Oscar flies back to the club, he hears a&nbsp;
dancer telling Mario that Linda is just using him.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:59.840 --> 00:10:04.400
